cientists and researchers, to recognize significant achievements in science around the world, by publishing scientific manuscripts. The manuscripts that fulfill the scholarly standards of innovative and latest issues are based on interdisciplinary. Insan Akademika Publications is an institution founded academicians who are affiliated with the<a href=\"http://www.uinsgd.ac.id/\" target=\"_blank\">State Islamic University of Sunan Gunung Djati Bandung</a>, <a href=\"http://www.uniga.ac.id/\" target=\"_blank\">University of Garut</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.sttgarut.ac.id/\" target=\"_blank\">Technology College of Garut.</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>IJBAS</strong>\r\n\r\nThe International Journal of Basic and Applied Science (IJBAS) is a multidisciplinary peer-reviewed journal that will be published four issues per year (quarterly) by Insan Akademika Publications. IJBAS is dedicated to increasing the depth of the subject across disciplines with the ultimate aim of expanding knowledge of the subject.\r\n\r\nIJBAS is an on-line and open access journal. One key request of researchers across the world is unrestricted access to research publications. Open access gives a worldwide audience larger than that of any subscription-based journal and thus increases the visibility and impact of published works. It also enhances indexing, retrieval power and eliminates the need for permissions to reproduce and distribute content. IJBAS is fully committed to the open access initiative and will provide free access to all articles as soon as they are published.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Aims</strong>\r\n\r\nIJBAS aims to publish papers of high quality and strives to promote scholarly debate across a broad international coverage of the subject with a flexible editorial policy, accepting submissions in any of the areas covered by the journal scope. IJBAS seeks to provide a unique and worldwide forum for communication between researches, experts and policymakers to exchanging research, views, concerns, as well as innovative ideas in the form of original papers.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\"><img src=\"http://www.insikapub.com/images/Logo%20UNIGA%20color.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" border=\"0\" /></td>\r\n<td align=\"center\"><img src=\"http://www.insikapub.com/images/Logo%20UIN.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"90\" height=\"155\" border=\"0\" /></td>\r\n<td align=\"center\"><img src=\"http://www.insikapub.com/images/Logo%20STTG%20biru.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"115\" height=\"115\" border=\"0\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','About Us','','publish','open','open','','about-us','','','2014-12-14 23:08:33','2014-12-14 23:08:33','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=11',0,'page','',0),(12,1,'2014-12-14 23:08:33','2014-12-14 23:08:33','<h2 class=\"item-page-title\">About Us</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Insan Akademika Publications</strong>\r\n\r\nInsan Akademika Publication is a non-profit organization established and dedicated to enhance cooperation and coordination among scientists and researchers, to recognize significant achievements in science around the world, by publishing scientific manuscripts. The manuscripts that fulfill the scholarly standards of innovative and latest issues are based on interdisciplinary. Insan Akademika Publications is an institution founded academicians who are affiliated with the<a href=\"http://www.uinsgd.ac.id/\" target=\"_blank\">State Islamic University of Sunan Gunung Djati Bandung</a>, <a href=\"http://www.uniga.ac.id/\" target=\"_blank\">University of Garut</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.sttgarut.ac.id/\" target=\"_blank\">Technology College of Garut.</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>IJBAS</strong>\r\n\r\nThe International Journal of Basic and Applied Science (IJBAS) is a multidisciplinary peer-reviewed journal that will be published four issues per year (quarterly) by Insan Akademika Publications. IJBAS 