hical or minor clerical errors, no changes will be made in the manuscript at the proof stage, because IJBAS publishes articles online to attract a wide range of audience, authors will have free electronic access to the full text (in both HTML and PDF) of the article. Authors can freely download the PDF file from which they can print unlimited copies of their articles.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Author Fees</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAuthor(s) are required to pay Article Publication Fee of US$ 50 for 10 pages of a manuscript. There are no additional charges for color images. Publication of an article in the IJBAS is not contingent upon the author\'s ability to pay the charges. Neither is acceptance to pay the handling fee guarantees that the paper will be accepted for publication.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAfter properly adjusting with IJBAS Template send your manuscript to: <a href=\"mailto:editor@insikapub.com\">editor@insikapub.com</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>PROCEDURE</strong>\r\n\r\nThe procedure for publishing of manuscript in the picture below:\r\n<table align=\"left\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.insikapub.com/images/procedure2.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','Author Guideline','','inherit','open','open','','51-revision-v1','','','2014-12-22 00:37:09','2014-12-22 00:37:09','',51,'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=52',0,'revision','',0),(53,1,'2014-12-22 00:37:33','2014-12-22 00:37:33','','Libraries','','trash','open','open','','libraries-3','','','2014-12-22 00:41:09','2014-12-22 00:41:09','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=53',0,'page','',0),(54,1,'2014-12-22 00:40:30','2014-12-22 00:40:30','','Libraries','','publish','open','open','','libraries','','','2014-12-22 00:40:30','2014-12-22 00:40:30','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=54',0,'page','',0),(55,1,'2014-12-22 00:40:30','2014-12-22 00:40:30','','Libraries','','inherit','open','open','','54-revision-v1','','','20